---
/**
 * TransferForm — Four Winds Roots Pharmacy
 * PHIPA-safe prescription transfer request form.
 * Collects: from-pharmacy info, patient details, medications, consent.
 *
 * PHIPA / COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS (see design/compliance-checklist.md):
 * - Explicit informed consent checkbox with plain-language explanation
 * - HTTPS-only POST to a compliant backend (TODO: choose backend — Netlify Forms or server function)
 * - Minimal data collection — only what's needed to process the transfer
 * - No health data stored client-side or in browser storage
 * - Honeypot field for spam prevention (aria-hidden, not visible to users)
 * - Success state confirms receipt; failure state provides phone fallback
 *
 * TODO: Wire up form action to a PHIPA-compliant backend before go-live.
 * TODO: Have the consent language reviewed by the owner/OCP before publishing.
 * TODO: Test with screen readers (NVDA/JAWS + VoiceOver) before go-live.
 */
import PhoneLink from './PhoneLink.astro';
---

<!--
  Online transfer form temporarily DISABLED. It collected PHIPA-protected health data but had no
  compliant backend wired. Until a PHIPA-safe vendor is selected
  (see research/phipa-vendor-comparison.md), we direct patients to call/fax/visit instead.
  The full original form markup is preserved in git history — restore it once a backend exists.
-->
<div class="pharmacy-form-cta" role="note" aria-labelledby="transfer-cta-heading">
  <h3 id="transfer-cta-heading">Transfer your prescriptions — call, fax, or visit</h3>
  <p>
    Online transfer requests are coming soon. In the meantime our pharmacy team can start your
    transfer in a couple of minutes — we'll contact your current pharmacy for you.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Call us:</strong> <PhoneLink /> — please have your current pharmacy's name and phone
      number, and your medication names, handy.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Fax us:</strong> (416) 398-6745</li>
    <li><strong>Visit us:</strong> 3932A Keele St, North York, ON M3J 1N8</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="pharmacy-form-cta__action">
    <PhoneLink class="btn btn-call" display="Call (416) 398-8200" />
  </p>
</div>
